{"tid":688832,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[歐遊] hea遊法國蘇格蘭","createTime":"2018-06-03T14:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T15:49:06.000Z","uid":5819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b70fcaab25f0e1d4da8a63c91439e8b34733a0f2","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"小弟同條女都係第一次衝出亞洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  今次揀左法國同蘇格蘭，計埋飛嘅時間全程總共14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  喺香港來回巴黎，途中會喺巴黎飛去愛丁堡，喺蘇格蘭留左8日，中間去左isle of skye 3-day tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，出發！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n<br />\n搭完成13差唔多14個鐘嘅長途機之後，我地朝早7點半左右就到咗巴黎，落機嗰吓真心有少少興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔好彩嘅事已經馬上發生，我個喼其中一隻碌已經俾人掟撚爛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻去叫airline出返張證明，又搞咗一大輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌個喼真係好撚難拉，第一日就搞啲咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住就去入境<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/223529_c270eb7dd0e8b6b2e46e7b8efb3a1362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F223529_c270eb7dd0e8b6b2e46e7b8efb3a1362.jpg&h=1466a37c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地用bno，所以2條友都冇印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地揀咗搭巴士出city center, 因為我地嗰時驚搭rer會俾人老笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搭巴士出去都要個零鐘，其間我地2個都攰得滯忍唔住訓著咗，overall其實搭巴士都算安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於出到市區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/223744_365827bfb4dc6a8eedae87269a810331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F223744_365827bfb4dc6a8eedae87269a810331.jpg&h=b9679db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行埋去airbnb附近都差唔多到check in time, 呢個時候check吓email啦，又有第二件唔好彩嘅事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個host話要遲2個鐘先check得in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬，搭完長途機已經攰到仆街，本身諗住即刻上去放低個爛9喼就休息，屌依家又要搵地方hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後去咗附近supermarket坐低食野同買呢幾日嘅糧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCheck in咗之後就煮野食，然後2條友都瞓死咗，差唔多天黑先醒返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求其落咗街附近行吓，day 1就咁完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9228cecbc4d2aa272556e394791f967d419576","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"改一改個格式先，好似有少少難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031f73495dcb56bd162049c915a9a5b4768d8468","tid":688832,"uid":161865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"巴打我過兩日都落巴黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eb840400a5399d2f147c350d6eac40938b1054","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n<br />\n一早5點零就醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n硬係諗住香港時間係11點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日嘅行程都係喺paris睇啲熱門景點<br />\n8點就出發，第一站去咗聖母院<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/225750_c4576d9aeba7592aafb3820ca81fa58d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F225750_c4576d9aeba7592aafb3820ca81fa58d.JPG&h=2e163bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能我地早得滯，條街勁少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入聖母院唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/230030_63e4bcd4c9dfffa94fe6d505369fbbd5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F230030_63e4bcd4c9dfffa94fe6d505369fbbd5.JPG&h=3cc08abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/230036_0ecfdda0b299da30a7cc521683bedf09.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F230036_0ecfdda0b299da30a7cc521683bedf09.JPG&h=cd361f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行咗一個圈出返去門口影相, 已經排哂長龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就去羅浮宮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/230137_4f60411d8c2495ba6534697b89125eda.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F230137_4f60411d8c2495ba6534697b89125eda.JPG&h=67bad277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地2個都對藝術品冇乜興趣，所以我地淨係去打吓卡就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行去羅浮宮嗰時遇到問卷黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁no no no之後佢地就冇再so我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/230423_d5577df06ba39b19839992ad1a35b7ca.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F230423_d5577df06ba39b19839992ad1a35b7ca.JPG&h=365aa7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影完羅浮宮，我地去咗好出名嘅outlet村<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/230547_0b4a218c4aac2671e59121f32cc06691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F230547_0b4a218c4aac2671e59121f32cc06691.jpg&h=addd099e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女買到野，我就幫佢影下相算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行完再返去行吓bnb附近，再返去煮野食，咁又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c009034f0bf407e14cebd2046f217f84cca56255","tid":688832,"uid":61267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"isle of skye 推介依幾個位<br />\n<br />\nfairy pool<br />\n<img src=\"https://scotlandexpert.files.wordpress.com/2017/01/fairy-pools-last-shot-of-bigger-pool.jpg?w=672\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscotlandexpert.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F01%2Ffairy-pools-last-shot-of-bigger-pool.jpg%3Fw%3D672&h=b52c09b3&s={SIZE}\" /> ,<br />\n<br />\nquiraing<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.earthtrekkers.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Quiraing-Isle-of-Skye-1163x775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.earthtrekkers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FQuiraing-Isle-of-Skye-1163x775.jpg&h=cf5beaf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同the old man of storr<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.photographylife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/AJT_7148-Edit-Edit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.photographylife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FAJT_7148-Edit-Edit.jpg&h=f9a4c04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 幾年前獨自scotland 流浪 其中有10日去左isle of skye<br />\n<br />\n一生難忘"},{"pid":"1636f04302fd9ddbb10773196d12ae02a2cb8ab1","tid":688832,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>isle of skye 推介依幾個位<br />\n<br />\n利申 幾年前獨自scotland <span style=\"color: red;\">單車流浪</span> 其中有10日去左isle of skye<br />\n<br />\n一生難忘</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8a26ad8f4b679f2fb30c7a988209b183dac113a2","tid":688832,"uid":40026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"