 />\n啱啱打漏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來Day 2食完夜晚之後<br />\n條女要求出去睇Eiffel Tower<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/004456_c6b59f9bc969489ada10e9a501b30105.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F004456_c6b59f9bc969489ada10e9a501b30105.JPG&h=9a23a6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴哂腳架諗住影夜景<br />\n點知等極都未天黑<br />\n最後我地都廢事排隊上個塔<br />\n求其打吓卡就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫我慳返幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都算係呢個trip其中一個遺憾<br />\n就係睇唔到Eiffel Tower著燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbb3f56cdad31e2f400d51019f0b51eca97213a","tid":688832,"uid":109513,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"留名。<br />\n太多表情，打字夠㗎啦清。"},{"pid":"2512785ffdc04c806710efcd9e767178acd0f7fe","tid":688832,"uid":136047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"096907625548e28c0dfd5eceb3128f0d383a6565","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"續Day 2<br />\n<br />\n啱啱打漏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來Day 2食完夜晚之後<br />\n條女要求出去睇Eiffel Tower<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/004456_c6b59f9bc969489ada10e9a501b30105.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F004456_c6b59f9bc969489ada10e9a501b30105.JPG&h=9a23a6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴哂腳架諗住影夜景<br />\n點知等極都未天黑<br />\n最後我地都廢事排隊上個塔<br />\n求其打吓卡就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫我慳返幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都算係呢個trip其中一個遺憾<br />\n就係睇唔到Eiffel Tower著燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0