pload/2018/06/04/004939_d5736197c7e2214b970d28c20edcd06c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F004939_d5736197c7e2214b970d28c20edcd06c.JPG&h=11b9b025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實本身係想去個個都話靚嘅colmar<br />\n但由於喺paris過去要好耐同好貴<br />\n所以揀咗呢個同colmar有少少似嘅城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭咗個零鐘就到咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/005352_b6c3372584815cf65ef106296fe072c1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F005352_b6c3372584815cf65ef106296fe072c1.JPG&h=e24e5e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好靚好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/005512_22458677a4c63f6dbcaf6b14e9d8ac4e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F005512_22458677a4c63f6dbcaf6b14e9d8ac4e.JPG&h=dca1b8b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/005516_78edaad337a8d5f9ea6446bdcd498712.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F005516_78edaad337a8d5f9ea6446bdcd498712.JPG&h=4db12c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做狗好過做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/005737_9cb80b4bdfe83a9d89df8e160a7df9dc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F005737_9cb80b4bdfe83a9d89df8e160a7df9dc.JPG&h=8f745628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/005742_154ab3153a7237b3689ca88d66745014.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F005742_154ab3153a7237b3689ca88d66745014.JPG&h=75a0a72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實都係睇吓建築咁<br />\n<br />\n但之後去咗個唔知咩教堂<br />\n又係免費參觀<br />\n我地覺得靚過聖母院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/010225_1e44f6ec9b009476cc1696d5dcdff70e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F010225_1e44f6ec9b009476cc1696d5dcdff70e.JPG&h=b70503e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/010136_ec443ebb43b4a7edb3209680cf05fa6a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F010136_ec443ebb43b4a7edb3209680cf05fa6a.JPG&h=9dd7a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/010138_86a7290a7f91652017e804378529ae50.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F010138_86a7290a7f91652017e804378529ae50.JPG&h=4c754a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/010139_d782d97848e10cd5329ebe5c5ce311b3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F010139_d782d97848e10cd5329ebe5c5ce311b3.JPG&h=753bb66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後都係周圍行吓, 食吓野<br />\n等夜晚巴士返paris<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢度一日遊ok<br />\n如果喺度住一晚應該會幾悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8530b8e6ac04b79de252bf26caadb2bb2eb6ce5","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T17:08:23.000Z","msg":"你地睇啲打直嘅圖有冇打橫咗？<br />\n我用電話睇係打直，電腦睇就頭已側<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8273b92cf9129fbd087cddc35b26b1d727f3ce2b","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bbb3f56cdad31e2f400d51019f0b51eca97213a","tid":688