65","tid":688832,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T23:43:46.000Z","msg":"羅浮宮地下個商場有個倒掛既金字塔<br />\n你地無去到影相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你同你女友係咪學生？<br />\n學生入去係唔洗錢架<br />\n（學生證佢望下就算，唔會深究係咪EU既學校）<br />\n唔洗錢入去望下Lisa姐都好啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e69cafe004a8c71055487645d4272e38051998f","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6eb194634e3e2290df0eb757f278cb8ff11a65","tid":688832,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T23:43:46.000Z","msg":"羅浮宮地下個商場有個倒掛既金字塔<br />\n你地無去到影相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你同你女友係咪學生？<br />\n學生入去係唔洗錢架<br />\n（學生證佢望下就算，唔會深究係咪EU既學校）<br />\n唔洗錢入去望下Lisa姐都好啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:29:00.000Z","msg":"有去影，懶揀相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係學生啦，grad咗幾年"},{"pid":"719bc60a3dbfde5cd20e1e0ab36191f5a2956111","tid":688832,"uid":5819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"Day 4<br />\n<br />\n朝早煮完早餐之後就執喼<br />\n今晚就會飛去愛丁堡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncheck out咗之後就走去就近嘅火車站寄存行李<br />\n唔洗拉住個爛9喼周圍走<br />\n<br />\n寄存完就去參觀凱旋門<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/234119_ba589df897ea38b4c61fba8073500886.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F234119_ba589df897ea38b4c61fba8073500886.JPG&h=ffb918ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/234121_1f005fc71639de8f2a70b9adc19cb77e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F234121_1f005fc71639de8f2a70b9adc19cb77e.JPG&h=cc2d8838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/234124_e18d3a0fb36f14717797f598cf7c72bb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F234124_e18d3a0fb36f14717797f598cf7c72bb.JPG&h=96292d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再去條好出名嘅香榭麗舍街行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/234205_7ec04be6f85620d9520054a5c51083d6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F234205_7ec04be6f85620d9520054a5c51083d6.JPG&h=8883acfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入親d名店都無人so我地 <br />\n可能一睇就知我地係window shopping<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我地諗住去行老佛爺百貨<br />\n行去嘅途中就見到有個門口寫住雞那咁大隻老佛爺百貨<br />\n我地以為到咗就入去<br />\n點知一入就傳出濃濃嘅蝗味<br />\n原來成間野係為大陸人而設<br />\n一批批大媽坐哂喺度<br />\n連啲員工都係全部講蝗話<br />\n我地頭也不回即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來行前多2步就會見到真正嘅老佛爺百貨<br />\n<br />\n其實喺paris呢幾日都無見到好多大陸人<br />\n唔知係咪佢地覺得巴黎自由行好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但老佛爺呢條街係佢地啲團嘅drop off point<br />\n即刻冇哂mood行<br />\n所以我地入去行咗個圈都走人<br />\n<br />\n寄埋postcard<br />\n我地就出發機場飛愛丁堡<br />\n搭火車途中撞正罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有驚無險總算上得切飛機<br />\n夜晚10點半左右就到埗<br />\n又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就會全程玩蘇格蘭啦"}]}